categories: Category:Alliance to Restore the Republic awards

nodes.text: The Golden Wings was the fourth embellishment of the Kalidor Crescent, the highest honor awarded by the Alliance to Restore the Republic. The Kalidor Crescent was awarded for extreme acts of heroism and gallantry against an overwhelming force. The Golden Wings were given after a live individual performed a fifth instance of heroism and gallantry and had previously been awarded the Bronze Cluster, the Silver Talons, and the Silver Scimitar. It was a set of solid gold wings that were placed on the kalidor.
